author: pirakapro
title: Star wars the clone.... car?
review:
This set is very cool! The car looks like it could be some next gen. Ferrarie! It looks the same color as the new clone wars box's! The launcher works well but if you put the car in the wrong way the car and launcher will run away! now the pros and cons



               pros:
   
                 cool colors
                 pull back motor!
                 lots of cool, new ,09 pieces
                 cool stickers! 
             
                 cons: 
 
                 motor doesnt work good on carpet
                 some pieces on the side and frount break off easy if it hits a wall 

                        a very good set!
